snippet.title: SONIC LEGENDS - CHAO DIRECT 2024 TRAILER
snippet.description:
We've been hard at work this past year updating our content from last year's demos to make this celebration of the creatives the best it can be!

While we can't provide a release date at this time, keep our accounts updated when SONIC LEGENDS: CHAPTER 1 is set to release!
